      "options": {
        "content": "## Tunnel Self-Healing Monitor\n\n**Auto-recovery:** O sistema verifica a saúde dos túneis a cada 30s. Após 2 falhas consecutivas, reinicia o serviço automaticamente (máx. 3 restarts/hora).\n\n**Túneis monitorados:**\n- **cloudflared-rpa4all** — Cloudflare Tunnel (dns/www/openwebui/grafana.rpa4all.com)\n- **nginx-proxy** — Nginx reverse proxy (porta 8090)\n- **openwebui-docker** — OpenWebUI container (porta 3000)\n- **grafana** — Grafana container (porta 3002)\n- **dns-doh-proxy** — DNS over HTTPS proxy (porta 8453)\n\n**Endpoints:** Prometheus `:9110/metrics` | Status `:9111/status` | Audit `:9111/audit`",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
